{"tid":415235,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［缺堤］落地港女嫁陸IT男，夫單程證獲批過新生","createTime":"2017-09-26T23:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T02:28:58.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2c6dffeaddab90840abaa8036dd2e9b1b63ee83f","tid":415235,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T23:03:54.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】任職美甲師、現年41歲的黃女士（Mandy）於2012年初，透過交友網認識來自北京、今年53歲的吳先生，二人一拍即合，交往一年後共諧連理。Mandy表示欣賞丈夫學歷高、不吸煙，「並非一般認識的內地人」。從事資訊科技行業的吳先生今年5月獲批單程證，現已開展新工作，期望在香港有更好發展，毋須在內地「凡事講關係」。<br />\n<br />\n求助立法會議員 毋須每季續簽雙程證<br />\n<br />\n新婚不久後，內地來港的雙程證政策改變，吳先生不能以為期一年的商務簽證來港，需每3個月奔走京港兩地辦理雙程證，加上他突然失業，為婚姻蒙上陰影。其後，Mandy向工聯會立法會議員麥美娟求助，麥美娟為她致信北京有關部門，吳先生最後獲准每年續簽一次雙程證，生活壓力下降，夫妻間爭執亦隨之減少。<br />\n<br />\n來港收入減 毋須「凡事講關係」<br />\n<br />\nMandy表示，丈夫讀書時期家境並不富裕，全憑自己努力掙錢到英國修讀資訊科技碩士學位。吳先生現於觀塘區從事「老本行」，雖然月入大不如前，只有約1.5萬元，但Mandy說，丈夫不太喜歡內地職場「凡事講關係」的文化，希望在港能有更好的前景。<br />\n<br />\n對於有調查指出，逾半受訪者樂意在粵港澳大灣區長遠定居，Mandy表示，丈夫樂意以香港為長遠居所，加上她的父親為長期精神病患者，需要家人照顧，Mandy表示不會離棄父親到內地生活。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170927/s00002/1506449533249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170927%2Fs00002%2F1506449533249&d=ET79mwu14G5d3JvAXnBCiLZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=3db8b487\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170927%2Fs00002%2F1506449533249&h=24b9a794\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170927/s00002/1506449533249</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/070236_f6db7d033f0989862331a43584e0693e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F070236_f6db7d033f0989862331a43584e0693e.jpg&h=b5a8f44d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遲d應該會有內地男為單程證騙婚<br />\n跟住係香港食其他高質港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dff510f35890aee4a7590101ee4eef67394a510","tid":415235,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T23:07:16.000Z","msg":"過橋抽板"},{"pid":"21474379f1fda450ebcccdeb63b44d81ebaeb9d0","tid":415235,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T23:07:27.000Z","msg":"英國科技碩士，我只諗到 unisoft x NCC<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5767987b4a66bf2dc19985aee57c749f2137ddd9","tid":415235,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T23:09:08.000Z","msg":"又係明報<br />\n維穩不遣餘力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a1cede4fddcbadfbfa89057912bdf06e67bd85","tid":415235,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T23:10:13.000Z","msg":"北京廢中(失業)"},{"pid":"2ef9529ac7b94be6ebf351464c20adcfc3b40fe9","tid":415235,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T01:21:58.000Z","msg":"呢條北嫂咁似上面開髪型屋果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e61c699799329b714eea6b6ebbff3d934ae70d7","tid":415235,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T01:31:03.000Z","msg":"d 大陸人吹到自己國家有幾好, 一有機會就即刻逃離自己祖國發展 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201943081b4c078625a73c575c8695b3a2d77967","tid":415235,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T02:26:19.000Z","msg":"中資入侵，你點知港中企唔講裙帶關係？"},{"pid":"c579fae3fbdd086a7e8c35541c947223fae4a990","tid":415235,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T02:28:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d 大陸人吹到自己國家有幾好, 一有機會就即刻逃離自己祖國發展 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊有逃離? 香港都係中國一部分嘛"}]}